From a7f99a2280bc369e7a74183a0704fbfc11a14bba Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Venkat Chimata <venkat@nearhop.com>
Date: Tue, 7 Apr 2026 16:02:15 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] hostapd / ubus: avoid banning clients before per-BSS ubus
 object is ready

There could be some scenarios where bss is created but
ubus is not inited yet. If we try to access variables like
ubus.banned, it would lead to hostapd crash.

This new check for the existence of ubus object prevents
the hostapd crash.

Fixes WIFI-15268

Signed-off-by: Venkat Chimata <venkat@nearhop.com>
---
 ...ng-clients-before-per-BSS-ubus-objec.patch | 39 +++++++++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 39 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 package/network/services/hostapd/patches/zzz-019-ubus-avoid-banning-clients-before-per-BSS-ubus-objec.patch

diff --git a/package/network/services/hostapd/patches/zzz-019-ubus-avoid-banning-clients-before-per-BSS-ubus-objec.patch b/package/network/services/hostapd/patches/zzz-019-ubus-avoid-banning-clients-before-per-BSS-ubus-objec.patch
new file mode 100644
index 0000000000..5f33893087
--- /dev/null
+++ b/package/network/services/hostapd/patches/zzz-019-ubus-avoid-banning-clients-before-per-BSS-ubus-objec.patch
@@ -0,0 +1,39 @@
+From ae969a531bf001001a410065597824afcbb50851 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
+From: Venkat Chimata <venkat@nearhop.com>
+Date: Tue, 7 Apr 2026 15:45:19 +0530
+Subject: [PATCH] hostapd / ubus: avoid banning clients before per-BSS ubus
+ object is ready
+
+There could be some scenarios where bss is created but
+ubus is not inited yet. If we try to access variables like
+ubus.banned, it would lead to hostapd crash.
+
+This new check for the existence of ubus object prevents
+the hostapd crash.
+
+Signed-off-by: Venkat Chimata <venkat@nearhop.com>
+---
+ src/ap/ubus.c | 5 ++++-
+ 1 file changed, 4 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)
+
+diff --git a/src/ap/ubus.c b/src/ap/ubus.c
+index 8baffa3..5bf3dba 100644
+--- a/src/ap/ubus.c
++++ b/src/ap/ubus.c
+@@ -523,9 +523,12 @@ hostapd_bss_del_client_cb(struct hostapd_iface *iface, void *ctx)
+ 
+ 	hwaddr_aton(blobmsg_data(tb[DEL_CLIENT_ADDR]), addr);
+ 
+-	for (i = 0; i < iface->num_bss; i++)
++	for (i = 0; i < iface->num_bss; i++) {
++		if (!iface->bss[i]->ubus.obj.id)
++			continue;
+ 		hostapd_bss_ban_client(iface->bss[i], addr,
+ 				       blobmsg_get_u32(tb[DEL_CLIENT_BAN_TIME]));
++	}
+ 
+ 	return 0;
+ }
+-- 
+2.34.1
+
-- 
